2016-06-13  Werner Koch  <wk@gnupg.org>

	gpg: Un-deprecate option --auto-key-retrieve.
	+ commit 9e126af215143fddbdc3949681abb9ffdb9153bb
	* g10/gpg.c (main): Remove deprecation warning.

