	(gpg2_SOURCES): Add tofu.h and tofu.c.
	(gpg2_LDADD): Add $(SQLITE3_LIBS).
	* g10/tofu.c: New file.
	* g10/tofu.h: New file.
	* g10/options.h (trust_model): Define TM_TOFU and TM_TOFU_PGP.
	(tofu_db_format): Define.
