	+ commit 40a914a2e3052847b49c4b5e8ac8538e97efd18a
	* scd/iso7816.h (struct pininfo_s): Remove MODE and add FIXEDLEN.
	* scd/app-dinsig.c (verify_pin): Initialize FIXEDLEN to unknown.
